the walls start to crumble, exposed to the world, when the wind
burns my face and the smoke burns my eyes, I can't ever cry, I
can't every cry.  You're gonna help to make me somebody;
you're gonna help to open my eyes.<P>

<HR align="center" width="85%"><P>

