something.<P>

<HR align="center" width="85%"><P>

 Here's something completely off the Everquest subject.  In your schooling or past ever run into a person by the name of Bob Koch?  He used to
babysit my kids and had a talent for 3D art.  He trained at the University that Disney runs and apparently was so talented, had many high income job
offers before he graduated.<P>

 From what I understood there are very few of your talent who can conceptulize art into 3D and having beta tested computer graphics and videoconfercing for the Air Force (yes, long before your time) I can only offer you compliments on all the work you've done in a game I enjoy in leisure time.  Keep up the good work!!<P>

 Ann

<P> <P><b><i>
<font face="Georgia" size="4" color="#9F3215">
Milo Says:
</font></i></b><BR>

   Sorry, I don't know anyone named Bob Koch.  Whoever he is,
I'm sure he's more talented than I, and actually I think that any decent
artist should be able to create three-dimensional art, be it formed as
computer graphics, sculpture, architecture, or whatever have you.
Many thanks for your compliments, all the same!<P>

